Developer Terms of Use
des:
Moe and Jenna Abdou interview a highly influential roster of thought leaders, authors, founders, creatives, and senior executives to deconstruct the hidden insights that only those who are building breakthrough ventures can reveal. For eight years now, 33voices has engaged closely with founders and senior executives to identify interesting & pressing challenges that give rise to thoughtful dialogue with contributors who not only think differently, but who represent the frontiers of knowledge in business, culture and lifestyle.
NOTE:
As soon as you open/launch the podcast, you will be playing the latest episode by default, but you can always find something more specific. Read HOW TO USE instructions below

HOW TO USE:
To Get Started: Say "Alexa, open ‘thirty three voices’”.

Next/Previous:
— [While Episode Is Playing] = “Alexa, next”
— [While Episode Is Playing] = “Alexa, previous”

Fast Forward:
If you want to skip ahead, you can say "Alexa, ask ‘thirty three voices’ to fast forward 2 minutes"

Rewind:
if you want to go back, you can say "Alexa, ask ‘thirty three voices’ to rewind 30 seconds"

Specific Episode:
You can also use ‘Episode No’ to play specific episodes
